Albert Gran https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Albert_Gran 0 Albert Gran (August 4, 1862 – December 16, 1932) was a Norwegian-born American stage and film actor. He is most associated with his appearance in drama and light comedy films. Albert_Gran ( August_4_,_1862 – December_16_,_1932 ) was a_Norwegian-born_American_stage_and_film_actor .
